---
/**
 * Notice banner that explains the ✦ sparkles badge — shown on every
 * scripture page so users learn what the AI auto-matching badge means.
 */
import Icon from "./Icon.svelte";
---

<p class="ai-match-notice">
  <Icon client:visible icon="sparkles" size={14} strokeWidth={1.7} />
  <span>표시는 AI가 자동 검출한 다른 경전의 유사 절입니다. 오류가 있을 수 있으니 댓글로 알려주세요.</span>
</p>

<style>
  .ai-match-notice {
    margin: 0.6rem 0 1.2rem;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.85rem;
    background: var(--color-secondary-bg);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-secondary);
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .ai-match-notice :global(svg) {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
</style>
